title: Dark Phone Blue GO SMS Theme

extendedInfo.description: ++ Now just $1.99! Enjoy! ++** Note this theme requires GO SMS Pro (Free on Android Market): http://bit.ly/tHqrr4Match this theme with (see last screenshot)* Dark Phone GO Keyboard: http://bit.ly/GU6BkQ* Dark Phone GO Contacts: http://bit.ly/LU4pPxFeatures* High quality, crisp graphics* Unique blue gradient accent* Stark contrast for optimum visibility* iPhone-inspired SMS bubbles* Optional custom ICS font!Install* Select done, return to GO SMS, menu, themes, and activate your new theme!Activate the font* Go into GO SMS settings, Appearance and Scan for Fonts.* Once finished, select the font "DarkPhoneFont [GO SMS Dark Phone Theme]" within the customization for Conversation List, Conversation and PopUp, and save to whatever you want.Enjoy!* Let us know what you think in the comments!Have questions?** As we are unable to respond to comments, feel free to get in touch with us through email, Facebook and TwitterFollow us for our latest themes!* Twitter (@aBbtdesigns): http://bit.ly/xqfEl1* Facebook (aBbtdesigns): http://on.fb.me/yO5ULmaBbtKeywords: colorful, black, crisp, sleek, gloss
